  "keyFeatures": [
    "Self-correcting memory with SQLite and FTS5 search",
    "Orchestration patterns: Command > Agent > Skill architecture",
    "18 hook events for lifecycle management",
    "5 specialized agents (planner, reviewer, scout, orchestrator, debugger)",
    "11 modular skills for workflow optimization",
    "Multi-phase development (Research > Plan > Implement > Review)",
    "Parallel worktrees for zero dead time",
    "80/20 review pattern with quality gates",
    "Cross-agent support (Claude Code, Cursor, 32+ agents via SkillKit)",
    "Split memory system for complex projects"
