    "/search - Search learnings by keyword",
    "/list - List all stored learnings",
    "/parallel - Parallel worktree setup",
    "planner agent - Break down complex tasks",
    "reviewer agent - Code review and security audit",
    "scout agent - Confidence-gated exploration",
    "orchestrator agent - Multi-phase workflows with memory",
    "debugger agent - Systematic bug investigation",
    "SessionStart hook - Load learnings from database",
    "PreToolUse hook - Quality gate reminders",
    "PostToolUse hook - Check for console.log, TODOs, secrets",
    "SubagentStart/Stop hooks - Agent lifecycle logging",
    "TaskCompleted hook - Quality gate on completion",
    "PermissionRequest hook - Flag dangerous operations"
